<div class="container p-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class=" mx-auto">
            <h1>{{links.nombre}}</h1>
            <h6>Small scale of MVP: {{links.descripcion}}</h6>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <center>
                    <h4>Irrigation Statuts: {{links.estatus}}</h4>
                    <p>Apagado: OFF</p>
                    <p>Encendido: ON</p>         
                        <form action="/sisris/panel/1{{!links.id}}" method="POST">
                            <button type="submit" name="estatus" value= "Encendido" class="btn btn-primary m-4"><center>ON</center></button>
                            <button type="submit" name="estatus" value= "Apagado" class="btn btn-primary m-4"><center>OFF</center></button> 
                        </form> 
                    </center>    
                </div>
                {{!<a href="/sisris/invitar/{{links.id" role="button">+ Añadir colaboradores</a>}}
            </div>      
            <div>
                <h1>Live Stream</h1>
                <p>The blue light means the irrigation is on!</p>
                    <img src="/sisris/last.jpg" id="cam" width="320"/>
                    <script>
                        setInterval(() => {
                            document.getElementById("cam").src = "/sisris/last.jpg?t=" + Date.now();
                        }, 500);
                    </script>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<p>The following is the variety of data we can measure in a real crop to provide the information that our Model of Smart Recommendations needs to calculate the best irrigation schedule</p>
    <div class="card-body">
        <center><h2>Soil Data</h2></center>
        <h5>Nitrogen: {{links.n}} mg/Kg</h5>
        <h5>Phosphorous: {{links.p}} mg/Kg</h5>
        <h5>Potasium: {{links.k}} mg/Kg</h5>
        <h5>Electric Conductivity: {{links.ec}} microSiemens(μS)</h5>
        <h5>Potential of Hydrogen (pH): {{links.ph}}</h5>
        <h5>Temperature: {{links.soil_temp}}°C</h5>
        <h5>Humidity: {{links.soil_hum}}</h5>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        <center><h2>Weather Data</h2></center>
        <h5>Solar Radiation: 6.2 kWh/m^2</h5>
        <h5>Wind Temperature: {{links.temp}}°C</h5>
        <h5>Wind Humidity: {{links.hum}}</h5>
    </div>
</div>
